tourBios.otherInfo: 2009 WVIAC Player of the Year while at the University of Charleston.
tourBios.prYrSeason: Earned non-exempt status with rounds of 74-71-70-76 at the 2012 Fall Qualifying School. Qualified for both the Jamieson WFCU Windsor Roseland Charity Classic and The Great Waterway Classic in 2012, finishing T40 at The Great Waterway Classic.

dyn.dynResults: His best finish on the PGA TOUR Canada was T40th in 2012 at the The Great Waterway Classic.
dyn.dynStats: He ranks T98th in Best YTD Par or Better Streak on the PGA TOUR Canada.
